<li>"<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2014/sep/24/english-votes-english-laws-absurdity-separatist">Why English votes for English laws is a kneejerk absurdity</a>". <i>The Guardian</i>. 24 September 2014.</li>
