<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2">
<h2 id="Notable_former_students">Notable former students</h2>
<span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Vernon_Bogdanor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Notable former students"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span>
</div>
<p>In addition to David Cameron, Bogdanor's former students include <a href="/wiki/Kate_Allen_(Amnesty_International)" title="Kate Allen (Amnesty International)">Kate Allen</a>, <a href="/wiki/Camilla_Cavendish" class="mw-redirect" title="Camilla Cavendish">Camilla Cavendish</a>, <a href="/wiki/Diane_Coyle" title="Diane Coyle">Diane Coyle</a>, <a href="/wiki/Guy_Spier" title="Guy Spier">Guy Spier</a> as well as <a href="/wiki/Toby_Young" title="Toby Young">Toby Young</a>.<sup class="noprint Inline-Template Template-Fact" style="white-space:nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources. (February 2019)">citation needed</span></a></i>]</sup></p>
